SUMMARY:The Teds and Cousins Maine Lobster
DESCRIPTION:Live Music & Food Truck at the Vineyard in Davis \n Friday\, May 22 | 5–8pm\nKick back and start your weekend the Great Bear way—with a glass of wine in hand\, vineyard views all around\, and a relaxing evening filled with music\, food\, and good company. \nWe’ve got another beautiful Friday night lined up featuring live music from The Teds and delicious seafood favorites from Cousins Maine Lobster. Sip\, relax\, and settle into an easygoing evening under the vines—the perfect way to welcome the weekend.\n Ticket Includes: Glass of Wine Live Music\n Music by The TedsWe’re excited to welcome back The Teds Band to the winery! This talented four-piece band brings all your favorite oldies to life with upbeat\, danceable tunes guaranteed to keep the good vibes flowing all evening long.\n Food by Cousins Maine LobsterCome hungry! Cousins Maine Lobster will be onsite serving up delicious chowders\, lobster rolls\, and seafood sandwiches packed with flavor. Please support this fantastic local business—no outside food permitted.\n Great wine\, live music\, fresh seafood\, and vineyard sunsets… sounds like the perfect Friday to us.\nWe can’t wait to see you there!
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/the-teds-and-cousins-maine-lobster/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards 24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitdavis.org/wp-content/uploads/Highway128PressTrip_GreatBearVineyards_2024_MaxWhittaker_12-Copy-scaled-OoIRnT.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
