LAST-MODIFIED:20260520T173104Z
UID:10002861-1779539400-1779553800@visitdavis.org
SUMMARY:What Your Nose Knows: A Wine Sensory Afternoon at Great Bear Vineyards
DESCRIPTION:What Your Nose Knows: A Wine Sensory Afternoon at Great Bear Vineyards in Davis \n Saturday\, May 23 12:30–4:30pm\nMost of us drink wine. Far fewer of us truly taste it.\nJoin us at Great Bear Vineyards for a one-of-a-kind sensory experience designed to unlock the hidden language of wine — and train your palate like a pro.\nLed by renowned winemaking consultant and UC Davis lecturer Zoran Ljepovic\, this immersive afternoon workshop will take you beyond “I like this wine” to understanding exactly why you like it. Using a professional Wine Aroma Kit and wines from the Great Bear cellar\, you’ll explore the fascinating aromas and flavors that define exceptional wines.\n During this hands-on experience\, you’ll learn: How to taste wine like a professional The difference between primary\, secondary & tertiary aromas How fermentation\, aging\, and barrel time shape flavor How to identify common wine faults with confidence Structured sensory evaluation techniques used by experts\n The afternoon also includes a guided tasting of six or more wines from the Great Bear portfolio\, featuring whites\, rosé\, and reds.\nWe’ll follow the classic: See →  Swirl →  Sniff →  Sip →  Spit\nPlease arrive fragrance-free (no perfume\, cologne\, or scented lotions) so every nose in the room can perform at its best!\n Even better: all profits benefit DEVO\, a student-led nonprofit working alongside the UC Davis Department of Viticulture & Enology to support future wine industry professionals.\nWhether you’re a curious beginner or a devoted wine lover\, this is an unforgettable afternoon of discovery\, education\, and delicious wine.
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/what-your-nose-knows-a-wine-sensory-afternoon-at-great-bear-vineyards/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards 24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://visitdavis.org/wp-content/uploads/5-23-26-Thumbnail-FOblnp.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
