SUMMARY:Geoffrey Miller and Italian Brother’s Pizza
DESCRIPTION:Live Music & Food Truck Night at the Vineyard at Great Bear Vineyards in Davis \n Friday\, May 29 5–8pm\nKick off your weekend vineyard-style with an evening full of live music\, delicious wood-fired pizza\, and a glass of wine in hand! \nJoin us for a relaxing night surrounded by beautiful vineyard views as acclaimed West Coast Country & Western artist Geoffrey Miller brings the soundtrack for the perfect Friday evening. Inspired by legends like Merle Haggard\, Buck Owens\, Dwight Yoakam\, Ray Price\, and George Jones\, Geoffrey’s authentic honky-tonk sound has earned national recognition and topped the Alt Country radio charts with albums All Night Honky Tonk Man and Leavin’ 101.\n Come hungry!Italian Brother’s Pizza will be serving up authentic wood-fired pizzas made with fresh\, high-quality ingredients and cooked to perfection in a traditional wood-fired oven. From classic favorites to specialty creations\, every slice is packed with flavor.\n Ticket Includes: Glass of Wine Live Music\nBring your friends\, grab a seat\, sip your favorite wine\, and settle in for an easygoing evening of music\, food\, laughter\, and vineyard vibes.\nWe can’t wait to welcome you for another unforgettable night at the winery!
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/geoffrey-miller-and-italian-brothers-pizza/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards 24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitdavis.org/wp-content/uploads/Great-Bear-Vineyards_23GBV-drone-scaled-zK0eUQ.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
